r\">/</span>tinker <span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span> <span class=\"token constant\">DONE</span>\n</span><span class=\"code-line\">  livewire<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>livewire <span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span> <span class=\"token constant\">DONE</span>\n</span><span class=\"code-line\">  nesbot<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>carbon <span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</